{"title":"Osteomielitis-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/Osteomielitis-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Osteomielitis","guid":"z5vypED7zQjlZNlqVnE-qw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Osteomielitis","guid":"Wcj1W_q_ZKvugMSiCIZ2ZA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Definición:","guid":"p_6EJ7C7PBOh1ryaBzt20w","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Infección del hueso ⟶ Vía hematógena (siembra desde foco remoto)\\No exógena (expansión desde tejido cercano) (1).","guid":"l1nHkihiK2GQDPKdtsVMOA","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Etiología:","guid":"LCgNwSV990V8ro8Y6UlbUQ","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• Patógeno + frecuente: Staphylococcus aureus (1).","guid":"0HuNfHT9sLlk1jI_5fRwdw","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"• Factores\\Nde riesgo:","guid":"yqGfrgeKpzVvp_zWag6-xw","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• Trauma.","guid":"EbQincW-_xEcVRT8ZiPQxg","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• Implantes quirúrgicos.","guid":"jmJ-SJWQONQjJw72p07WnQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"• Inmunosupresión.","guid":"OFfMQUT4PcXUzLbC4QM9eQ","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"6","text":"• Mala perfusión tisular (1).","guid":"PRveRmiiKQ3I29PoWMZtyw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"1","text":"Clasificación:","guid":"1GUfwTvsfoYOGeBDMO2iVQ","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• Aguda: ⬆︎ signos inflamación local (dolor, eritema, edema, calor)\\N+ síntomas sistémicos (fiebre, escalofríos) (1).","guid":"8EG5Ms1ufhzWuvpC7lCx5A","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"• Crónica: Curso prolongado en adultos; requiere tto prolongado (1).","guid":"Z70NcPE4YUp4IkwtPNkDfg","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"1","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"GOcLh9pkAaIseuDk8e4idg","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• Clínico: Signos locales + sistémicos (1).","guid":"VHm-bwoTxZAbOr38NuxzCQ","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• Laboratorio: ⬆︎ VSG, PCR.","guid":"NuR2t-CUueiSgizItfOscg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"• Imágenes: RX, RMN.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"• Biopsia: Confirmación y cultivo (1).","guid":"vPvSpmVU4c0_iIhQH94qzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"1","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"2xLXYPEx1Do-Qr3RS_H-4Q","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"• ATB empírico: Indicado solo en sepsis o infecciones rápidas;\\Nesperar cultivos para tto dirigido (1).","guid":"dePdp28dLog-iAFcB58erA","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"• Quirúrgico: Remoción de hueso necrótico, abscesos,\\Ncuerpos extraños infectados, fístulas (1).","guid":"pMl_R66Q2qVMomfwDMXIwg","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"1","text":"Pronóstico:","guid":"FxpjzfHGlJWDGEiCPn9r7w","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• Adultos: Curso crónico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"• Niños: Recuperación rápida y completa (1).","guid":"7SCXGgsi7p6h0U5Z8kqWdA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"Definiciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• Osteitis: Término general para inflamación del hueso (1).","guid":"6IgCwhil9Qch5zHKMX8jNA","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"• Osteomielitis: Infección del hueso (1).","guid":"UX5MRy7kWtuHeoTeFvCUeA","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"• Incidencia: ∼ 20 por 100, 000 habitantes (1).","guid":"7wgr7SfKyXf47YLGkcUiNQ","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"• Osteomielitis hematógena:","guid":"rtk3uVv6pugHXU9KEXGhTA","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"•  • común en niños y adolescentes (1).","guid":"InOElLCS2uWzsxpSy9r_xw","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"• ⬆︎ incidencia en adultos por ⬆︎ osteomielitis vertebral (1).","guid":"NHiun9r61LGYlsvZ0-M5Zw","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"28","text":"• Osteomielitis exógena: + común en adultos (1).","guid":"7GxIjwRV-dFyjoF2MFwxeg","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"0","text":"Etiología:","guid":"bl1NE6XlxUDG1ixHIkn6pw","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Hematógena (endógena): Diseminación hematógena de patógeno (2).","guid":"xkpk5saB4JnfywwFvCC5tg","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"• Exógena: Diseminación de bacterias desde el entorno\\N(generalmente múltiples patógenos) (3).","guid":"-OuzPBCJg1nytvtwZqzz0g","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"34","text":"• Postraumática: Infección tras lesión profunda (herida penetrante,\\Nfracturas abiertas, lesión grave de tejidos blandos) (3).","guid":"u7DvdYe7SeG5nzBaEyfjFw","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"34","text":"• Contigua: Diseminación desde tejido adyacente (3).","guid":"jBjyjco7o34nWujhQKHRVQ","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Ej. úlcera del pie infectada en pacientes con DM.","guid":"ldsrbvGGOjjFP8Pi2EHLhA","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"34","text":"• Iatrogénica (infección postoperatoria de prótesis) (3).","guid":"egng7PseKRKEITUGwW97MA","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"0","text":"Factores de\\Nriesgo:","guid":"oueesvTfR3vB1JlqkMPgLQ","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"• Locales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• Mala perfusión tisular.","guid":"CfovUZa-r2B99y0c44pNpQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"• Fracturas abiertas.","guid":"bzcRo84GXm6NtX6LG1IUyQ","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"• Lesión grave de tejidos blandos (3).","guid":"Tv4LCcyy7EeoJQEsNXOE1w","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"41","text":"• Sistémicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"• Inmunosupresión.","guid":"GeDG1lSXFdYnFSuw1UFdDg","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"• Enfermedades sistémicas (ej. DM, aterosclerosis) (3).","guid":"GwdHRBWAJ_xGqrEFdZBarg","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"• Uso IV de drogas (3).","guid":"THSPTmpCai2yzVsSnPMSJA","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"41","text":"• Microbianos: Patógenos altamente virulentos (3).","guid":"sB2X8Uy_aqUBc-EpTDrQOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"0","text":"Patógenos más\\Ncomunes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"• Staphylococcus aureus:\\N+ común (3).","guid":"SYWH86BD4FtwNiOv_wcsSA","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• Afecta niños, adultos, usuarios de drogas IV, pacientes con lesiones\\Nvertebrales, prótesis, DM con úlceras de pie y úlceras por presión (4).","guid":"kTc-uGeie6Ho20m9BRL-pg","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"51","text":"• Staphylococcus epidermidis: Asociado a prótesis (4).","guid":"cm9mXVfjFfJjBZUUJcrugQ","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"51","text":"• Streptococos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• Pacientes con DM, úlceras de pie, úlceras por presión, neonatos e infantes (4).","guid":"mczPLJpgPktQ6Hr5o4f-1A","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"51","text":"• Pseudomonas\\Naeruginosa:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Personas que se inyectan drogas, heridas punzantes plantares\\N(especialmente con calzado de suela de goma) (4).","guid":"DsBSxBizBM2A0kPxb8I6_g","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"51","text":"• Enterobacteriaceae (4).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"51","text":"• Salmonella: Pacientes con anemia falciforme (4).","guid":"UWZUKjpuuYFjApxcOgVNUg","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"51","text":"• Klebsiella: Pacientes con ITUs (4).","guid":"DQqMHnjjYeoSHA7JPC_8IA","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"51","text":"• Mycobacterium tuberculosis: Ver “espondilitis tuberculosa” (enfermedad de Pott) (4).","guid":"aWEDwpJn7Abyyi_sLZJeEA","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"51","text":"• Pasteurella multocida: Mordeduras de perros y gatos (4).","guid":"nmns38yIODK_SXawolHQsA","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"51","text":"• Hongos (ej. Candida): Pacientes inmunocomprometidos, usuarios de drogas IV (4).","guid":"z85cAD1ktzFmfyEbhbOYYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico de Osteomielitis\\N(no vertebral)","guid":"Z0Q4WsI1bruuSTLuY1Esog","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"• Signos de sepsis presentes: Iniciar manejo de sepsis\\Nsin esperar resultados de pruebas diagnósticas (1).","guid":"HwmYIDjw7OoY_XsrqSxtcw","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"• Estudios de rutina:","guid":"BJYF5tRFT5RA1zZkS5et4w","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• CBC: Trombocitosis, posible leucocitosis (2).","guid":"dXEWqMCNuSGMf9M-l0mIIA","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"• Marcadores inflamatorios: ⬆︎ CRP, ⬆︎ VSG\\N(sensibles pero no específicos) (2).","guid":"19sk8w6jFCLh5Mzkn7WT7A","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"• Hemocultivos:","guid":"ZR4AQOMaXAj5sYdVVXZLCg","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"•  • en osteomielitis hematógena (2).","guid":"50fatZ0oJhiaPTOG5GGsTQ","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"•  • en osteomielitis exógena (2).","guid":"VvjlnxW9Kw76I440IYl9Qw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"65","text":"• Rx: Elección de imagen adicional depende\\Nde características del paciente (1).","guid":"7tXXQb0Rk77xrnM1LP8UqA","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"65","text":"• Osteomielitis hematógena sospechada: Considerar estudios\\Nadicionales (ej. urocultivo, Rx tórax) según presentación clínica (1).","guid":"6y_wllTPcFosrN6F0Bd9HA","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"65","text":"• Imágenes y hemocultivos no concluyentes: Considerar\\Nbiopsia ósea con cultivos para confirmar diagnóstico (1).","guid":"SGhTNosLXDruVIgwt_fhYg","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"0","text":"Manejo en pacientes\\Nestables:","guid":"2aKTE-lCwFrD7Ky4tOqjRA","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"• Diferir ATB hasta obtención de hemocultivos y/o biopsia ósea (1).","guid":"7TfcMWCzpabk09yIL3y8sA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"• No retrasar ATB en pacientes con signos de sepsis (1).","guid":"euRKJsb7CZEPLIk_yQAU8A","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"0","text":"Estudios adicionales\\N(según necesidad):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"• Sepsis: Evaluación diagnóstica completa para sepsis (1).","guid":"5cAnuDtPSLaPuezlGHIiSg","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"• Heridas purulentas/senos: Considerar cultivo de material purulento (1).","guid":"_STmMb8_X9UaeVuHO-nXYw","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"0","text":"Imágenes de rutina:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• Rx:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"• Sensibilidad/especificidad: Bajas para osteomielitis (1).","guid":"mk80Cc8NlSTkIDHWXFEJng","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"• Indicaciones: Evaluación inicial y exclusión de diagnósticos diferenciales (1).","guid":"LR4nemyPRmFlyf9DTtcvTQ","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"• Hallazgos\\Ncaracterísticos:","guid":"fPoZmG2oJ4b4mJCX0O5_KA","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"• Osteomielitis aguda: No suele mostrar hallazgos patológicos (2).","guid":"-6lZBgQQ5k63do8cAHKSiA","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"• Osteomielitis subaguda/crónica: Destrucción ósea,\\Nformación de secuestro, reacciones periosteales (2).","guid":"zNtB_fxwdqTDFZZXB9OCew","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"82","text":"• RMN con/sin gadolinio IV:\\NEstudio + sensible (1).","guid":"dmJ0UGN5480KS5vKMTofRA","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"Bh5QA13RXq970DFO2HtJqQ","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"• Sospecha de osteomielitis aguda (evidencia\\Nde inflamación ≤ 5 días post infección) (3).","guid":"5idPE_Kz6mlJuCJsPisKnA","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"• Rx negativa pero alta sospecha clínica (3).","guid":"Gy2BfSLlZGHXyWYhKoXJqw","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"• Evaluación de la extensión de la osteomielitis (1).","guid":"y6oQbkF3z-_3oZzEGBsdmw","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"89","text":"• Hallazgos\\Ncaracterísticos:","guid":"f6TwMsRWNottPsXKueCYXg","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"• Osteomielitis aguda/subaguda: Destrucción cortical,\\Ninflamación de médula ósea, afectación de tejidos blandos (3).","guid":"dgUH2J8yFHJDpsyrnT6Mbg","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"94","text":"• Osteomielitis crónica: Cicatrización\\Nfibrótica de la médula ósea (3).","guid":"flIdcuGIqNtP4wGfYx_Amw","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"89","text":"• Desventajas:","guid":"EdfLWBnn1E7YTMvA0ppfCg","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"• Dificultad para diferenciar infección de inflamación\\N(ej. en pacientes postoperatorios) (3).","guid":"n-irqMXWdMa-oFWL50o1Gw","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"• Disminución de calidad de imagen\\Npor hardware quirúrgico (3).","guid":"UA6_aEGX6cg2d9N81YhC1A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"82","text":"Resumen:","guid":"hCrxxqdeDOwU5PiCOQEV5Q","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"• Rx: Recomendado como modalidad inicial por ser económica y útil para descartar\\Ndiagnósticos diferenciales, pero puede no detectar osteomielitis aguda (1).","guid":"HVqZr5vT_LirtrcS_93mTQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"0","text":"Imágenes en\\NCircunstancias\\NEspeciales","guid":"ssp8MNRZu53L7XkmJvkVGw","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"• Contraindicaciones\\Npara RMN:","guid":"vXOB5iLcQyvM90FIOWiEQQ","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"• Adultos: TAC con contraste (1).","guid":"RLQv1u5d43GqEbX2b4RxKQ","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"• Niños: Ecografía (1).","guid":"fr2V-T7-SOFe2eQtnbmVnw","children":[]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"102","text":"• Cirugía reciente\\No fractura:","guid":"ynKwJh0_ke3pLYS_YW_NWA","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"• Escintigrafía con leucocitos marcados (2).","guid":"VbFp8qnNzedj7TZ9P4vJGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"102","text":"• Hardware quirúrgico (que\\Nafecta la calidad de la RMN):","guid":"qhR47HZ7OiACC9lpxQF-xQ","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"• Escintigrafía ósea trifásica (2).","guid":"bBrUz8UWakKeVSzoY-Ywfg","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"102","text":"• Sospecha de absceso superpuesto\\N(posible drenaje):","guid":"yvZa8guLQYSe_UokXXM68A","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"• Ecografía (1).","guid":"1AfmC9MLelNFG5lsfgWDrA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"0","text":"Biopsia\\Nósea","guid":"h3wfqZBGg-6FauZmSITGJA","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"• Hallazgos de imagen y hemocultivos inconclusos (3).","guid":"mNsaZreoKGOV-zt77Yd7Jg","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"• Opciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"• Biopsia con aguja guiada por RMN/TAC.","guid":"90frBnkznBx4lRVNNPZ-ng","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"• Biopsia abierta (3).","guid":"wXt4h4QlBrSW2PktWv20XA","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"112","text":"• Momento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"• Antes de la administración de ATB, si es posible (4).","guid":"dwzIAQjqvv9gkoJJdYzAKw","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"112","text":"• Envío de muestras\\Npara:","guid":"d-nZhIsI9aKgHX6VtU5MiA","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"• Tinción de Gram y cultivos.","guid":"XW8SiK7l_1pzI3_4oy-vLA","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"• Histología (4).","guid":"GLa_CnkQ5pmMRnLSYam0sg","children":[]}]},{"id":"123","parent":"112","text":"• Nota: La biopsia ósea con cultivos es la prueba confirmatoria para osteomielitis y debe realizarse a\\Nmenos que existan características de imagen típicas de osteomielitis y hemocultivos positivos (4).","guid":"M9vtHwikMAs4LJBrxP3HqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos Diferenciales\\Nde Osteomielitis","guid":"a4p0YRgksuojr1rUidVqIA","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"• Artritis\\Nséptica:","guid":"eWAA41RNPTtLeEgDZk2AIQ","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• Infección de la articulación (vs. osteomielitis, rara vez afecta la metáfisis) (1).","guid":"Z4e-YaaGZmNz-nC7OHlnZg","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"• Puede ocurrir secundaria a osteomielitis en infantes (1).","guid":"9bYE-jgjBNV1ABME6E_nZQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"124","text":"• Necrosis ósea avascular (1).","guid":"nHc7NJ_08NM5hpvXFCDROA","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"124","text":"• Tumores óseos\\Nmalignos:","guid":"OjeSwDZRWXSaAx3Qb0Ww3w","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"• Ej.: Sarcoma de Ewing, osteoma osteoide (1).","guid":"VAHbH1ZepwxAImNXCClY0A","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"124","text":"• Tumores\\Nóseos benignos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"• Ej.: Quiste óseo (1).","guid":"0FRAo5ilSfOIunrUUl1CTA","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"• Fractura (1).","guid":"DTF8VGLmx6P0ZegYqY8dPw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento de\\NOsteomielitis no Vertebral","guid":"7u-VQk6SFBFYxCH5whcqDA","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"Enfoque\\NGeneral:","guid":"d0NpYJTV54jmTP2ghbf8nA","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"• Todos los\\Npacientes:","guid":"f5j42Mz71JjKAJCAAhXrtw","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"• Ingreso para ATB IV; consulta con especialistas en enfermedades\\Ninfecciosas para guiar la elección de ATB (1).","guid":"Qacklxq_Ogy6AijYcWt3Qg","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"• Signos de sepsis o infección grave/progresión rápida:\\NAdministrar ATB empírico (1).","guid":"x_2lG9qz_YWUUDPaW_mkQw","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"• Otros pacientes: Administrar ATB dirigido\\Nuna vez disponibles los cultivos (1).","guid":"PsGwVa2KYigT4sWBcXJgeQ","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"136","text":"• Manejo del dolor y tto de soporte para\\Noptimizar la curación ósea (1).","guid":"BBdC3TkiDcUcXqp8cLtZfg","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"136","text":"• Considerar el seguimiento de marcadores\\Ninflamatorios para monitorear la respuesta al tto (2).","guid":"4snkTA4PzqRMxeiQIHNbAA","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"135","text":"• Osteomielitis\\Nhematógena:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"• Identificar y tratar la\\Ninfección subyacente (3).","guid":"PMjL5Epk2oeb9OL5ufpZoQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"135","text":"Consultas:","guid":"vk1rLEMyikuI2qODuSP_Kg","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"• Manejo de comorbilidades (ej. pie diabético, enfermedad de células falciformes) (1).","guid":"lfTXOz64p5SwFEAtLpl4aQ","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"• Cirujanos (ortopédico\\No vascular):","guid":"nZgrp4026D7zslW6WoFYEw","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"• Determinar necesidad\\Nde cirugía según:","guid":"KmSL3x59VLASpNqdSOOgcQ","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"• Extensión de la enfermedad.","guid":"Fae5FUMcQVZ9Sc1cZVV88w","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"• Presencia de hardware quirúrgico.","guid":"FAX9RH_UVrDliFI3Km3Nsg","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"147","text":"• Comorbilidades del paciente (4).","guid":"qIPXfUVoinL3rljZ5jvNtA","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"134","text":"Tratamiento\\NEspecífico:","guid":"HfjiyNTs5sSI-0_RoAkuJA","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"• Osteomielitis hematógena aguda: Generalmente se trata solo con ATB (5).","guid":"D7CepsDSwttCkjypNWmu8w","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"151","text":"• Osteomielitis aguda por diseminación\\Ncontigua y osteomielitis crónica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"• Requiere desbridamiento\\Nquirúrgico del tejido infectado (5).","guid":"3rsPSQSAHrFBWhVnsBD23A","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"0","text":"Terapia Antibiótica\\Npara Osteomielitis","guid":"4jGObb2THXW7afkBF_titQ","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"Consideraciones\\NGenerales:","guid":"pCCsQ9-ephpEZa_IQ0KLDg","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"• La terapia ATB empírica rara vez es necesaria (1).","guid":"-OfIcbNLLe8p1ufZnDc-vA","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"• Iniciar la mayoría de los pacientes directamente\\Ncon ATB dirigido según resultados de cultivos (1).","guid":"LZYH2sZNCozhQJrnRfUJ3g","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"156","text":"• Considerar cambio a ATB oral tras curso inicial de ATB IV (2).","guid":"0Wpf0F_d8Sp4zxodMmHdCA","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"156","text":"• Duración del tratamiento: 4–8 semanas (2).","guid":"E_MBLt9ufjTU3kO0UskADg","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"156","text":"• En casos raros, pacientes no aptos para cirugía pueden\\Nrequerir terapia ATB supresiva a largo plazo (2).","guid":"7B4l4arXNfoBX03rPOXR6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"155","text":"Biopsia Ósea:","guid":"dY0AaQKSlengrst1xcFp4g","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"• Obtener preferentemente antes de iniciar ATB\\Npara maximizar el rendimiento diagnóstico (3).","guid":"Sjtb-IdDoC0C7Hdm6fF0fg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"0","text":"Terapia Antibiótica Empírica\\Npara Osteomielitis:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"Indicaciones:","guid":"uGA-xRTc_-WrsVYgY4wfXg","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"• Signos de sepsis (4).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"165","text":"• Infección grave o de rápida progresión (4).","guid":"ndlxUTzqYnWYh3f9h7rsIw","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"165","text":"• Considerar en osteomielitis del pie diabético (4).","guid":"5cQWkVVBKKcW1eeLnsbcDg","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"164","text":"Regímenes Empíricos\\Npara Adultos:","guid":"-zQuFjAf7Jny7BQHPiM95g","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"• S. aureus (ej. con vancomicina DOSIS) (5).","guid":"iKETUjJpl7_UGcZxm-5iyA","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"• Bacilos gramnegativos, incluyendo Pseudomonas;\\Nregímenes recomendados incluyen (5):","guid":"Sc-CwT6QeL8oPJPCFid35A","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"• Meropenem DOSIS (5).","guid":"ILrksOiQ1D_n8mJT8iG5ug","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"171","text":"• Cefepime DOSIS +\\NMetronidazol DOSIS (5).","guid":"Nd8iEhtCVhhxyrJEUkgGJQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"174","parent":"164","text":"Precaución:","guid":"MMbDWs1G3HCGVjpEwH8G7Q","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"• Evitar combinar vancomicina con piperacilina-tazobactam debido al alto riesgo de\\Nnefrotoxicidad, a pesar de la cobertura eficaz contra S. aureus y Pseudomonas (6).","guid":"oriRd784bZuny2303m3SDw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"0","text":"Terapia Antibiótica Dirigida\\Npara Osteomielitis","guid":"SXVDUVog6zbYKJ2RoeNlyg","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"Patógeno → Primera línea\\N→ Alternativa","guid":"Tz_sglP-XeNz7tEPPKm1mQ","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"• Staphylococcus\\Nspp.","guid":"ku72omx4ziINugBO6piOFw","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"• MSSA:","guid":"CzjV0xDPMxAsR2Hm1zbjWQ","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"• Primera línea: Nafcilina DOSIS,\\NOxacilina DOSIS, Cefazolina DOSIS.","guid":"ywN-u5NKY3p7LS_xstl1eQ","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"• Alternativa: Ceftriaxona DOSIS,\\NVancomicina DOSIS (1).","guid":"7RyQ1T42XTCcwIhCt80WSA","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"178","text":"• MRSA:","guid":"84KCzBgF4ibIrqhCOtdB5A","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"• Primera línea: Vancomicina DOSIS.","guid":"qmLeTrSVHVknavlTRdA96w","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"182","text":"• Alternativa: Daptomicina DOSIS, Linezolid\\NDOSIS, Clindamicina DOSIS (2).","guid":"zuYg13SGDtsoMrjb-K8h1w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"177","text":"• Enterococcus spp.","guid":"","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"• Penicilina-sensible:","guid":"9G0vtGbt3wfto3pfidAOCA","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"• Primera línea: Ampicilina DOSIS\\N(considerar añadir Gentamicina DOSIS) (3).","guid":"JC4gRw8HzmWBYG1nP7C7Rg","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"186","text":"• Alternativa: Vancomicina DOSIS, Linezolid DOSIS (2).","guid":"0ISP-hradvUwbNB6sL1Hgg","children":[]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"185","text":"• Penicilina-resistente:","guid":"_cYop0GqkaeOkb0VYm2MSw","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"• Primera línea: Vancomicina DOSIS.","guid":"ndpu-IUdS9TW0qdveBTTOg","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"189","text":"• Alternativa: Linezolid DOSIS (2).","guid":"3mENOY2QiRzQtTkyj3U3jQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"177","text":"• Enterobacteriaceae","guid":"","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"• Sensible a\\Nquinolonas:","guid":"e2XBoU42ALXnHwZ6CRHElQ","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"• Primera línea: Ciprofloxacino DOSIS.","guid":"2cFJ6tk8LabI7dnlLKvQaQ","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"• Alternativa: Ceftriaxona DOSIS (2).","guid":"hom-HBxbjmySNZ-Hx6Ipgg","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"192","text":"• Resistente a\\Nquinolonas:","guid":"Bo4wonMUEnDBggAcOfJFog","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"• Primera línea: Piperacilina/Tazobactam\\NDOSIS, Ticarcilina (2).","guid":"D7ehqIS75sCfGWxO58Ij0A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"177","text":"• Pseudomonas\\Naeruginosa","guid":"qn7Wfu8DS2HWTggoWoWDIQ","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"• Primera línea: Cefepima DOSIS, Piperacilina/Tazobactam DOSIS\\N(+ Ciprofloxacino DOSIS) (2).","guid":"ljUJ9hI1WCO4iqPdI27IbA","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"• Alternativa: Imipenem DOSIS, Meropenem DOSIS (considerar\\Nañadir aminoglucósido, ej. Gentamicina DOSIS) (2).","guid":"S8mzOKV4rFXh--8s1XFlSg","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"177","text":"• Estreptococos\\Nbeta-hemolíticos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"• Primera línea: Penicilina G DOSIS.","guid":"pnog_xJvRscejUIUA2wqXg","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"201","text":"• Alternativa: Clindamicina DOSIS, Ceftriaxona DOSIS (2).","guid":"sX2zzFA9Fh7ucJir8Hw8zw","children":[]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"177","text":"• Anaerobios","guid":"","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"• Primera línea: Clindamicina DOSIS, Ticarcilina.","guid":"2XUQURF8Fdy2yV1CBy9j8w","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"204","text":"• Alternativa: Metronidazol DOSIS, Cefotetan DOSIS (considerar añadir Rifampicina\\NDOSIS en pacientes con hardware quirúrgico/cuerpos extraños retenidos) (3).","guid":"yYKexKqn3wbRTfKPgwAPKA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"176","text":"Terapia de\\NSoporte:","guid":"_bNqoZkUHgupmkju6PUhUw","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"• Optimizar nutrición.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"• Tratar anemia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"207","text":"• Manejar comorbilidades (ej. DM).","guid":"y7xen2-Ew3FgjUK4e-mlPA","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"207","text":"• Tratar úlceras por decúbito asociadas.","guid":"YXI8cibMirPTuaQEHakNZQ","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"207","text":"• Manejo del dolor con analgesia, inmovilización\\Ndel área afectada, y fisioterapia (3).","guid":"z7T2uKkbuBhCNLyGVRPxWw","children":[]}]},{"id":"213","parent":"176","text":"Cirugía:","guid":"0CF73rL2VQVPn4XsHGeqQw","children":[{"id":"214","parent":"213","text":"• Manejar factores del paciente que pueden haber afectado la curación antes de la cirugía\\N(ej. anemia, mala nutrición) (4).","guid":"_dfUZG_IN1s2Wv6mgGK_6g","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"213","text":"• La decisión de cirugía debe hacerse en consulta con especialistas en enfermedades infecciosas.","guid":"lGiX-QuszcykRsHFyp2jsw","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"213","text":"• Continuar la terapia ATB postcirugía, incluso si el hueso ha sido desbridado con éxito (4).","guid":"MGfNtAM29jdIktNGxX6-nw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"217","parent":"0","text":"Intervenciones Quirúrgicas\\NPotenciales en Osteomielitis:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"• Osteomielitis\\Ncrónica:","guid":"-y_GCZLXj22dIMbFoUm-NQ","children":[{"id":"219","parent":"218","text":"• Desbridamiento de hueso y tejido necrótico.","guid":"2FxHa15g6UPerL7EV_gvsg","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"218","text":"• Considerar amputación en enfermedad severa (4).","guid":"4HQUuZgEuxlJfwhrAoKXDA","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"218","text":"• Osteomielitis aguda refractaria a tratamiento ATB (4).","guid":"ECfcZRCeJdxppnYmOLsQQA","children":[]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"217","text":"• Infección de prótesis\\Narticular o cuerpo extraño:","guid":"OlWZwWCzZL9wkuA6VvgaBQ","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"• Remoción para\\Npromover remisión (5).","guid":"Tq2kXQW2Ay4iRmeGHYfrZw","children":[]}]},{"id":"224","parent":"217","text":"• Osteomielitis\\Npostraumática:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"• Desbridamiento de heridas infectadas.","guid":"X-d1XYtjZctj1O1EAo1YeA","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"224","text":"• Puede requerir remoción de hardware quirúrgico (4).","guid":"uRZSXmvVyDEakgaSQnItmQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"227","parent":"217","text":"• Absceso superpuesto:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"228","parent":"227","text":"• Incisión y drenaje (4).","guid":"gf_PIkwaXtBvJ1p36pRFwA","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"217","text":"• Mala cicatrización de heridas o\\Nisquemia de extremidades:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"• Revascularización (5).","guid":"IEIsTHewcxHVkLmpS53GRg","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"• Considerar amputación en enfermedad severa (4).","guid":"bh3CMeMfcN9O1uhyD7p05g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"232","parent":"0","text":"Subtipos y Variantes\\Nde Osteomielitis","guid":"KF4mugUJ1_TRERLFFGA6QQ","children":[{"id":"233","parent":"232","text":"• Absceso de\\NBrodie:","guid":"bxGAQwoyCgmr16RD_Od_bg","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"• Definición: Osteomielitis subaguda caracterizada por un absceso intraóseo;\\Nafecta comúnmente el fémur distal y la tibia proximal (1).","guid":"Se9buzFf0g-_RuCg8ltDnw","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"233","text":"• Fisiopatología: Siembra hematógena desde un foco infeccioso distante ⟶ infección piógena subaguda o crónica del hueso\\N⟶ formación de tejido fibroso y de granulación alrededor del foco piógeno ⟶ absceso localizado (1).","guid":"zlLW92n4YicIFCYsdOF2kQ","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"233","text":"• Características\\Nclínicas:","guid":"MQoR_v2YIbN0rhYwgC9RIw","children":[{"id":"237","parent":"236","text":"• Frecuentemente asintomático o con síntomas leves.","guid":"bmtpCaEzcH8-98Efdfp77A","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"236","text":"• Dolor localizado (1).","guid":"dZABTFP3lhzpMr34sFZ7Yw","children":[]}]},{"id":"239","parent":"233","text":"• Diagnóstico: Lesión quística bien circunscrita, de pared gruesa en la metáfisis\\Ny epífisis de huesos largos en Rx y RMN con contraste (1).","guid":"Q2qVIkGh41mItz0JiHr_-g","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"233","text":"• Tratamiento: Drenaje quirúrgico y ATB (1).","guid":"GRF1mzKtie0s72wb8NZaYA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"241","parent":"0","text":"Complicaciones de\\NOsteomielitis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"• Infecciosas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"• Absceso.","guid":"KeF5YcnhUY4Sk_oUK8UajA","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"242","text":"• Sequestro.","guid":"Mgd_ZaU9jd4VE3D_IMV_qQ","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"242","text":"• Osteomielitis recurrente o crónica.","guid":"jsgAkfUxqEO_bDpLX79uFw","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"242","text":"• Piartrósis: infiltración de articulaciones cercanas.","guid":"x_E45j0kN1sc0cth_YvuwA","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"242","text":"• Tractos sinusales.","guid":"9UPbd35QtgRHWkR6EkqJrw","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"242","text":"• Celulitis.","guid":"CVrQFnGZdNGnsT9m3boO8w","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"242","text":"• Sepsis (2).","guid":"X1zV0bU50WFQvSYU05nZ8g","children":[]}]},{"id":"250","parent":"241","text":"• Mecánicas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"• Destrucción progresiva del hueso.","guid":"e5x6YWGm7Rv96sBnbl7PjQ","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"250","text":"• Fracturas patológicas.","guid":"FJBIUaSNN5KO6d56Tw2h6g","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"250","text":"• Pseudoartrosis, cicatrización ósea anormal (2).","guid":"bJat9nhopP8W8hN3ltbkHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"241","text":"• Malignas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"• Desarrollo de úlcera de Marjolin (2).","guid":"Ahp73T5HUMfww_QXjHYdCw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"256","parent":"0","text":"Pronóstico de la\\NOsteomielitis","guid":"rpf5NWxpPts_HAWj08XRBw","children":[{"id":"257","parent":"256","text":"• Osteomielitis\\NAguda:","guid":"0HYKADE9Xq95ZQZIBiwWeQ","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"• Recuperación rápida y completa es común en niños\\Nque reciben tratamiento antimicrobiano adecuado (1).","guid":"tZeBtR6MgrQIQFx4t7URuA","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"• En adultos, la osteomielitis aguda frecuentemente\\Nse transforma en osteomielitis crónica (1).","guid":"QNmzxKk7OHZXBPgoWYnCaw","children":[]}]},{"id":"260","parent":"256","text":"• Osteomielitis\\NCrónica:","guid":"z_nottxmY4tFE2_OwKQV6Q","children":[{"id":"261","parent":"260","text":"• Difícil de curar (2).","guid":"GPjzz0jfZ75cpItef-4ZYQ","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"260","text":"• A menudo requiere tratamientos quirúrgicos y\\Nantibióticos repetidos durante años o décadas (2).","guid":"AjIDA0DeoCeMrZGTsNNuww","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"260","text":"• En pacientes con diabetes o insuficiencia vascular, la\\Nprobabilidad de resolución completa es particularmente baja (2).","guid":"vTm0JxOzBrRJbEHu3O8L-g","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":263,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Infectología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Infectología","filename":"Osteomielitis-2024","id":"map_1168","resolved_references":[]}